CHEESE BLEND: CHEDDAR CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES, ANNATTO [COLOR]), IMITATION CHEDDAR CHEESE (WATER, RENNET CASEIN [MILK PROTEIN], PALM OIL, WHEY, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SALT, SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE, LACTIC ACID, NATURAL FLAVOR, SODIUM CITRATE, SORBIC ACID [PRESERVATIVE], TRISODIUM PHOSPHATE, ARTIFICIAL COLOR, GUAR GUM, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, ENRICHMENT BLEND [MAGNESIUM OXIDE, ZINC OXIDE, FERRIC ORTHOPHOSPHATE, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, RIBOFLAVIN, PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE, NIACINAMIDE, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, VITAMIN B12]). COOKED BEEF TOPPING: HAMBURGER (BEEF, SEASONINGS [SALT, SPICES, FLAVORINGS], WATER, TEXTURED VEGETABLE PROTEIN [SOY PROTEIN CONCENTRATE, CARAMEL COLOR]).
